Ghana’s Producer-Price Inflation Rate Rose to 17.2% in August

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-09-28T10:13:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/ghana-s-producer-price-inflation-rate-rose-to-17-2-in-august.html
Ghana ’s producer-price inflation
rate climbed to 17.2 percent in August, compared with a revised
13.9 percent a month earlier,  Grace Bediako , head of the Ghana
Statistical Service, told reporters in Accra today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
